‚úÖ Finance teams can identify fake invoices & payment diversion scams.
‚úÖ Payments are verified through dual authorization and vendor validation.
‚úÖ Reduced financial loss and phishing incidents.
‚úÖ Increased compliance with internal audit and fraud control frameworks.
‚úÖ Finance evolves from ‚Äútarget zone‚Äù to **secure transaction guardian.**

> ‚ÄúCybercriminals steal trust before they steal money ‚Äî verify everything.‚Äù üíº

